# Plugin Command Contract Templates

## Intent
Provide enforceable templates for plugin command contracts, access policies, and audit events.

## Required Template Set
- [201-plugin-command-schema-template.mdc](201-plugin-command-schema-template.mdc)
- [202-plugin-access-policy-schema-template.mdc](202-plugin-access-policy-schema-template.mdc)
- [203-plugin-audit-schema-template.mdc](203-plugin-audit-schema-template.mdc)

## Mandatory Usage
- Every plugin command surface must implement all three templates before release.
- Contract versions must be explicit and backward compatibility documented.
- Contract validation must run in CI before merge.

## Release Blockers
- Missing template implementation for any plugin command surface.
- Missing contract versioning or migration notes.